display="inline"><![CDATA[R]]></fr:tex> be a ring, let <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[M]]></fr:tex> be a module over <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[R]]></fr:tex>, let <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[R^{n}]]></fr:tex> be the finite-rank free module over <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[R]]></fr:tex>. Then
<fr:tex
display="block"><![CDATA[\mathop {\textrm {Hom}}\nolimits _{R}(R^{n},M)\cong  M^{\oplus  n}]]></fr:tex>
where <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[M^{\oplus  n}=\bigoplus ^{n}_{i=1} M=M\oplus  M\oplus …\oplus  M]]></fr:tex> is just the direct sum of <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[n]]></fr:tex> copies of <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[M]]></fr:tex>.</fr:p>
 
   
